Package: hdr
Title: Interface to the UNDR Human Development Report API
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Eric", "Persson", email = "expersso5@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a complete interface to the United Nations
    Development Programme Human Development Report API (<http://hdr.undp.org>). The API
    includes a large amount of human development data, including all the series used
    to compute the Human Development Index (HDI), as well as the HDI itself.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.3)
License: CC0
LazyData: true
BugReports: https://github.com/expersso/hdr
URL: http://hdr.undp.org ; https://github.com/expersso/hdr
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Imports: httr
Suggests: ggplot2,
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
